data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! MOTIVATED SELLER! BRING ALL OFFERS! This is a beautiful, spacious, and well maintained end-unit townhome in amenity-packed Highland Creek, Cross Pointe complex! It's a must see and will not last long! Natural light galore as windows are plenteous! Main level living including primary suite and laundry! Comes with a loft which can easily be used as a home office, workout space, theater room, play area for the kids, or however you so desire!  Lots of in-home storage areas including the primary suite professionally designed closet!  Convenient to shopping and major highways! This 3 bedroom, 2-1/2 bath home is a dream come true!
